00:49:53,664 --> 00:49:54,744
but I know because I get a cup of tea

418
00:49:55,024 --> 00:50:01,528
and I’ll be going like this have to pull myself and it will pass. Not very often.

419
00:50:04,023 --> 00:50:08,868
