428
00:51:10,308 --> 00:51:12,104
I get very angry with him.

429
00:51:12,378 --> 00:51:14,423
Recently, this is an issue for me,

430
00:51:14,664 --> 00:51:19,784
he doesn’t react and then he says to me why is this and why is that

431
00:51:20,058 --> 00:51:24,024
and he doesn’t do anything about it and he is so capable.

432
00:51:29,018 --> 00:51:35,403
